  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A little boy didn’t listen to his mother’s warnings that eating too much at night would cause nightmares. Now, he must face hordes of monsters and defeat the nightmare bosses to escape.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEFEAT THE NIGHTMARE BOSSES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face mini-bosses and nightmare bosses. Use your weapons and skills to win each battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.poster.avif?t=1745816199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.webm?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/cfb2a78edba930df41dbe1733964579d.mp4?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVE THE HORDES OF MONSTERS AND TRAPS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Withstand waves of monsters and deadly traps. Test your skills in increasingly difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.poster.avif?t=1745816199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.webm?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/729d59d7b829b74e1f51c69959e3c1a3.mp4?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHOOSE YOUR ARSENAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your arsenal with a variety of weapons and spells. Personalize your strategy and always be ready for the next enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.poster.avif?t=1745816199\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.webm?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663620/extras/0c8e79179c6920ca34a265abc1c2a867.mp4?t=1745816199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MAIN FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive hordes of monsters and traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect souls to acquire weapons and spells in the shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons and spells with unique effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip up to 4 weapons to defeat your enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip a magic spell to help in your battles</p></li></ul>",
